Content","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/107/14/s7/e/2"},"text":"“Any amount collected under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3018C/b"},"text":"section 3018C(b) of title 38","children":[],"tail":", United States Code (whether by reduction in basic pay under paragraph (1) of that section, collection under paragraph (2) of that section, or both), with respect to an individual who enrolled in basic educational assistance under section 3018C(e) of that title, during the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-11-01"},"text":"November 1, 2000","children":[],"tail":", and ending on the date of the enactment of this Act ["},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2001-06-05"},"text":"June 5, 2001","children":[],"tail":"], shall be treated as an amount collected with respect to the individual under section 3018C(e)(3)(A) of that title (whether as a reduction in basic pay under clause (i) of that section, a collection under clause (ii) of that section, or both) for basic educational assistance under section 3018C of that title.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
